msgid "ཨོཾ་ བཛྲ་ ས་ ཏྭ་ ཨཱཿ"
msgstr "OM VAJRA SATTVA AH "

msgctxt "05fcdfe6085641809675ff0a7672fcf5"
msgid ""
"ཞེས་ སྙིང་པོ་ འབྲུ་ དྲུག་པ་ ཉིད་ ཅི་ ནུས་ སུ་ བཟླ་བ་ ཀུན་རྫོབ་ རྒྱུ་␣འི་ "
"སྒྲིབ་ སྦྱོང་ དང །"
msgstr ""
"With the visualization, repeat the hundred syllable mantra OM VAJRA SATTVA "
"SAMAYA etc., and the heart mantra OM VAJRA SATTVA AH as much as you can. "
"This is the fictional causal practice. "

msgctxt "ac6fede85e514a05ba8ec432311d5419"
