"Resting in equipoise within the true nature is the superfactual, fruitional "
"purification of obscurations. "

msgctxt "cd5565a27bc94373b4621d985fe8b24e"
msgid "བཞི་པ་ ཚོགས་ བསགས་པ་ ནི །"
