"The heaps of the five lights of timeless wisdom awareness are arrayed. "

msgctxt "4da13e803b474cf39d4f742683d2586e"
msgid "གཞི་མེད་ སྤྲོས་བྲལ་ ཀུན་བཟང་ ཡབ་ཡུམ་ ལ་␣༔"
